\c 18
\s UJesu ufundisa ngokuthobeka langezikhubekiso
\p
\v 1 Ngalesosikhathi abafundi beza kuJesu, bathi: Kanti ngubani omkhulu embusweni wamazulu?
\v 2 UJesu wasebizela kuye umntwana omncane wammisa phakathi kwabo\x + 17.24. Mark. 9.33-37. Luka 9.46-48.\x*,
\v 3 wathi: Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Ngaphandle kokuthi liphenduke\x + Luka 22.32.\x* libe njengabantwana abancane, kalisoze lingene embusweni wamazulu.
\v 4 Ngakho lowo ozazithoba njengalumntwana omncane, nguye omkhulu embusweni wamazulu\x + 19.14. Mark. 10.14. Luka 18.16. Hlab. 131.2. 1 Kor. 14.20. 1 Pet. 2.2.\x*.
\v 5 Njalo loba ngubani owemukela abe munye umntwana omncane onje ebizweni lami, wemukela mina\x + 10.40.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Kodwa loba ngubani\x + Mark. 9.42. Luka 17.2.\x* okhubekisa omunye walaba abancinyane abakholwa kimi, kungakuhle kuye ukuthi ilitshe lokuchola elikhulu lilengiswe entanyeni yakhe, abesetshoniswa enzikini yolwandle\x + 5.29. 18.8,9.\x*.
\v 7 Maye kuwo umhlaba ngenxa yezikhubekiso\x + 13.41.\x*! Ngoba izikhubekiso zimele ukufika\x + Luka 17.1.\x*; kodwa maye kulowomuntu, esifika ngaye isikhubekiso\x + 26.24.\x*\x + Luka 17.1.\x*!
\v 8 Njalo\x + Mark. 9.43-47.\x* uba isandla sakho kumbe unyawo lwakho\x + 5.30.\x* kukukhubekisa, kuqume u\add ku\add*lahlele khatshana lawe\x + 18.8,9. 5.29.\x*; kungcono kuwe ukungena ekuphileni uyingini kumbe uyisiqhwala, kulokuthi ulezandla ezimbili kumbe inyawo ezimbili uphoselwe emlilweni olaphakade\x + 15.30.\x*.
\v 9 Futhi uba ilihlo lakho\x + 5.29.\x* likukhubekisa, likhuphe u\add li\add*lahlele khatshana lawe\x + 18.8,9. 5.29.\x*; kungcono kuwe ukungena ekuphileni ulelihlo elilodwa, kulokuthi ulamehlo amabili uphoselwe esihogweni somlilo\x + 5.22.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Qaphelani lingadeleli omunye walaba abancinyane\x + 18.2,6,14. 10.42.Zek. 13.7.\x*, ngoba ngithi kini: Emazulwini ingilosi zabo\x + Seb. 12.15. Hlab. 34.7; 91.11. Dan. 3.28; 6.22. Jobe 33.23. Luka 2.13. Heb. 1.14.\x* zihlala zibona ubuso\x + Esta 1.14. Luka 1.19.\x* bukaBaba osemazulwini\x + 7.11.\x*.
\v 11 Ngoba iNdodana yomuntu ize ukusindisa\x + 9.13. Luka 9.56; 19.10. Joha. 3.17; 12.47. 1 Joha. 4.14.\x* okwakulahlekile\x + 10.6; 15.24.\x*.
\s Imvu elahlekileyo
\p
\v 12 Licabangani\x + 17.25; 21.28.\x*? Uba umuntu othile elezimvu ezilikhulu, besekulahleka enye yazo, kazitshiyi yini ezingamatshumi ayisificamunwemunye lasificamunwemunye, ahambe ezintabeni ukuyadinga elahlekileyo?
\v 13 Futhi uba kungenzakala ukuthi ayithole, ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Uthokoza ngayo kakhulu kulalezo ezingamatshumi ayisificamunwemunye lasificamunwemunye ezingalahlekanga\x + Luka 15.4-7.\x*.
\v 14 Ngokunjalo kayisiyo intando kaYihlo osemazulwini\x + 7.11.\x* ukuthi kubhubhe abe munye walaba abancinyane\x + 10.42.18.2,6,14. Zek. 13.7.\x*.
\s Ukuphathwa kwabenza okubi
\p
\v 15 Kodwa nxa umfowenu ekona, hamba umsole phakathi kwakho laye lilodwa\x + Luka 17.3. Jak. 5.19,20. Levi 19.17.\x*. Uba ekuzwa, umzuzile umfowenu\x + 1 Kor. 9.19-22. 1 Pet.3.1.\x*;
\v 16 kodwa uba enga\add ku\add*zwa, thatha abe munye kumbe babe babili kanye lawe futhi, ukuze lonke ilizwi liqiniswe ngomlomo wabafakazi ababili kumbe abathathu\x + Dute. 19.15. Joha. 8.17. 2 Kor. 13.1. Nani 35.30.\x*;
\v 17 njalo nxa esala ukubezwa bona, tshela ibandla; uba esala ukuzwa lalo ibandla\x + 16.18. 1 Kor. 5.4,5; 6.1-6.\x*, kabe njengowezizwe\x + 6.7.\x*\x + Roma 16.17. 1 Kor. 5.9. 2 Thes. 3.6,14. 2 Joha. 10.\x* lomthelisi kuwe\x + 5.46,47; 9.10,11; 11.19; 21.31,32. Mark. 2.15,16. Luka 3.12; 5.30; 7.29,34; 15.1; 18.10.\x*.
\v 18 Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Konke elizakubopha emhlabeni, kuzakuba kubotshiwe ezulwini; njalo konke elizakukhulula emhlabeni, kuzakuba kukhululiwe ezulwini\x + 16.19.\x*.
\s Ukukhuleka kwabahlanganyelayo
\p
\v 19 Njalo ngithi kini: Uba ababili benu bevumelana emhlabeni loba ngaluphi ulutho abalucelayo\x + Mark. 10.35.\x*, bazalwenzelwa\x + 5.14. 1 Joha. 3.22.\x* nguBaba osemazulwini\x + 7.11.\x*.
\v 20 Ngoba lapho ababili kumbe abathathu ababuthene khona ebizweni lami, ngikhona lapho phakathi kwabo\x + 28.19.\x*.
\s Umfanekiso wenceku engelasihawu
\p
\v 21 UPetro wasemsondelela wathi: Nkosi, umfowethu uzangona kangaki, njalo ngimthethelela\x + 18.15.\x*? Kuze kube kasikhombisa yini\x + Luka 17.4. Jobe 5.19.\x*?
\v 22 UJesu wathi kuye: Kangitsho kuwe \add ukuthi\add* kuze kube kasikhombisa, kodwa kuze kube ngamatshumi ayisikhombisa aphindwe kasikhombisa\x + 6.14.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Ngakho umbuso wamazulu ufananiswa lomuntu \add oy\add*inkosi, owayethanda ukulandiselana lenceku zakhe\x + 25.19.\x*.
\v 24 Kwathi eseqalile ukulandisa\x + 25.19.\x*, kwalethwa kuye enye elomlandu kuyo \w wamathalenta\w** azinkulungwane ezilitshumi.
\v 25 Kodwa njengoba yayingelalutho lokuhlawula, inkosi yayo yalaya ukuthi ithengiswe\x + Levi 25.39.\x*, lomkayo labantwana bayo, lakho konke elakho, besekuhlawulwa\x + Neh. 5.5.\x*.
\v 26 Ngakho inceku yawa phansi imkhothamela, yathi: Nkosi, ngibekezelela, futhi ngizakuhlawula konke.
\v 27 Inkosi yaleyonceku yasisiba lesihelo yayikhulula, yayixolela umlandu.
\v 28 Kodwa yaphuma leyonceku yathola omunye oyinceku kanye layo, olomlandu kuyo \w wabodenariyo\w** abalikhulu, yambamba ya\add m\add*khama, yathi: Ngihlawula okufaneleyo.
\v 29 Ngakho oyinceku kanye layo wawa phansi ezinyaweni zayo wayincenga, wathi: Ungibekezelele, futhi ngizakuhlawula konke\x + 18.32. 8.5; 26.53.\x*.
\v 30 Kodwa yona kayivumanga, kodwa yasuka yayiphosela entolongweni, ize iwuhlawule umlandu.
\v 31 Kwathi abayizinceku kanye layo bebona izinto ezazenzakele badabuka kakhulu; beza babikela inkosi yabo konke okwakwenzekile.
\v 32 Inkosi yayo yasiyibizela kiyo yathi kiyo: Wena nceku embi, ngakuxolela wonke lowomlandu, ngoba wangincenga\x + 18.32. 8.5; 26.53.\x*;
\v 33 ngabe lawe kawumhawukelanga yini omunye oyinceku kanye lawe, njengoba lami ngakuhawukela?
\v 34 Inkosi yayo yasithukuthela yayinikela kubahlukuluzi, ize ihlawule konke okufaneleyo kuyo.
\v 35 Uzakwenza njalo kini laye uBaba osezulwini, uba lingathetheleli lowo lalowo umfowenu iziphambeko zabo ngenhliziyo zenu\x + Mark. 11.26. Jak. 2.13.\x*.